name: URLSessionTaskMetrics.ResourceFetchType
desc: The manner in which a resource is fetched.

items.name: case unknown
items.desc: The manner in which the resource was fetched could not be determined.

items.name: case networkLoad
items.desc: The resource was loaded over the network.

items.name: case serverPush
items.desc: The resource was pushed by the server to the client.

items.name: case localCache
items.desc: The resource was retrieved from the local storage.
